      <conflict id="TIMING_CONFLICT_BUDDY_ESTIMATE" with-fact="BUDDY_REPORTED_REMAINING_DAYS_55_83">Previously Buddy reported the remaining wait for Elder Heartwood's response (after one week elapsed) would be approximately 55–83 days. This passage states Elder Heartwood considered the question for four weeks and seven days (~35 days) and a messenger delivered a response—contradicting the earlier 55–83 day remaining estimate.</conflict>
